title: War of the Roses: He's Nicknamed Judas
description: Mia has learned some things about her boyfriend from his friends, including him being nicknamed Judas for something slimy he did 10 years ago.  She feels like he hasn't been as interested in her lately so she's wondering if he's up to his slimy ways again.
